## 2026-05-16 — switched ORM to raw SQL for the hot path
**why:** ORM was generating 14-join queries for 3-table lookups; perf tanked under load
**rejected:** ORM query hints (still magic), custom resolver (too much code for too little win)
**risk:** lose automatic migrations — added manual scripts in db/migrations/ to compensate
**tags:** db, infra, v1
